    "If that is the case, it may be meaningful to differentiate between the portion of spacetime allocation that corresponds to clean ancillae and the fraction that corresponds to dirty ancillae.",
    "Preparing Many Copies of Independent Quantum StatesThis section will show how we manage to utilize the novel encoding method we proposed in Sec.",
